Find CRP SNP

crp_snp <- subset(dat, chr == 1) %>%
  mutate(dist=abs(pos.exposure - 159682079)) %>%
  arrange(dist) %>%
  select(dist, SNP, pval.exposure) %>%
  {.$SNP[1]}
